    Used to define the allowed Combinations of Preselects.
    more than two combinations can be defined per row.
    Here i.E. we could write:
    <COMBINATION powder="true" sweetfoam="true" double="true"/> -> for products that support powder, sweet foam and double, all 3 preselections may be active at the same time
